stories.title: Australia sword England by 8 wickets
stories.summary: In an awe-inspiring performance, Australia inflicted a crushing defeat on England by an enviable margin of 8 wickets

stories.title: Australia coast to victory over England
stories.summary: An awesome display by Australia's batsmen condemned England to their 11th successive defeat in limited-overs cricket in a match that was totally dominated by Australia as they coasted to victory by eight wickets

stories.title: Australia on the verge of comfortable victory
stories.summary:
Australia's batsmen have made the last match before the NatWest Series final
on Saturday look like a practice game in preparation for the showdown with
Pakistan at Lord's on Saturday
